title: Attribute Extractor
description: Attribute Extractor I, Gu Shaoyang, have the ability to extract fused attributes. Extracting the savvy roots of countless geniuses, I am the top enchanting evildoer, a peerless arrogant. Combining countless low-grade primordial stones and inferior elixirs, I can make the best primordial stones and god-level elixirs. Now I just want to ask: when will I be invincible? ! ! Attribute Extractor I Can Extract Attributes Wǒ Néng Tíqǔ Shǔxìng Wo Neng Tiqu Shuxing 我能提取属性
